metadata.name: TCL Electronics Holdings Limited
metadata.description: TCL Electronics Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates as a consumer electronics company in the People's Republic of China, Europe, North America, and internationally. It operates through four segments: TV; Internet Business; Smart Mobile, Connective Devices, and Service; and Smart Commercial Display, Smart Home, and Other Businesses. The company manufactures and sells color television (TV) sets under the TCL brand; provides advertising, video-on-demand, and membership card services. It also engages in the manufacture and sale of smart mobile, smart connective devices, smart commercial display, smart home products, and other household products; trading of TV products, components, and white goods; research and development of software on smart TV devices, and mobile devices; and operation of the Internet platform, as well as distribution of mobile devices and components. The company was formerly known as TCL Multimedia Technology Holdings Limited and changed its name to TCL Electronics Holdings Limited in June 2018. The company is based in Sha Tin, Hong Kong. TCL Electronics Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of TCL Technology Group Corporation.
